      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:6:3:14:1",
      "text": [
        " سَأَلْتُهُ عَنْ عِتْقِ الْمُكْرَهِ فَقَالَ لَيْسَ عِتْقُهُ بِعِتْقٍ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, from Ibn Abu Umeyr, from Umar Bin Azina, from Zurara, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Ja’far<sup>asws</sup>, said, ‘I asked him<sup>asws</sup> about an emancipation of the coerced. So he<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘His emancipation is not with a (valid) emancipation’."
        ]
      }
